# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
"""
PsyArch Agent local runtime
===========================

This module is intentionally thin around ObservatoryApp. It gives the PA
prototype a local, auditable agent loop without changing the AP cognition
core: user text enters AP, AP runs ticks, a compact cognitive packet is built,
then an LLM or local fallback produces narrative thoughts and optional replies.
"""

